Questions Have Arisen Over The Safety Of Food Given To Remandees In Kayole And Soweto Police Stations Here In Nairobi. This Is After Reports Of Questionable Means Of Transporting Food Meant For The Remandees. And As Our Reporter Lofty Matambo Found Out, A Woman Contracted To Supply Food In The Two Police Stations In Kayole Has Employed A Deaf Man Who Uses Buckets To Carry The Food In Matatus.